Ethiopian birr strengthens against dollar . The Ethiopian birr strengthened against the dollar on Monday from last week , the central National Bank of Ethiopia ( NBE ) said . It quoted the birr at a mean rate of of 6 . 8010 against the dollar compared to 6 . 8530 last week . It said following a currency auction on June 28 that the applicable rate for all transactions outside the auction in the June 30 to July 6 period would be 6 . 8010 birr to the dollar . The central bank posted the birr at a mean rate of 11 . 3644 against the pound sterling from 11 . 4273 on Friday and 0 . 059423 against the yen from 0 . 060352 . 
